articles.title: Indonesian fishermen rescued off Australian coast after six days without food and water - CNN
articles.description: Eleven Indonesian fishermen were rescued by Australian maritime authorities from a tiny island after being stranded for six days without food or water, but there are fears nine others may have drowned.
